        <h1>Bosch Dishwasher Repair Los Angeles</h1>
        <p class="hero-sub">Factory-trained service on Bosch dishwashers — 100, 300, 500, 800 Series, and Benchmark. SHP/SHX/SHE model families. Full E-code diagnostic (E15 anti-flood, E22 filter, E24/E25 drain, E09 heater, E26 diverter). CrystalDry zeolite, PrecisionWash, AquaStop, Home Connect. Same factory platform as Thermador dishwashers.</p>
        <div class="hero-ctas">
          <a href="tel:+14243250520" class="btn-primary">☎ (424) 325-0520</a>
          <a href="/contact/" class="btn-outline">Book Online</a>
        </div>
